  "prompt": "What is the salary for an Android developer with 4+ years experience in Dublin, Ireland?",
  "response": "As of my last update, the salary for an Android developer with over 4 years of experience in Dublin, Ireland typically ranges between \u20ac50,000 and \u20ac75,000 annually. However, this can vary based on factors such as the specific employer, individual skills, the complexity of the projects involved, and the level of demand for Android developers at the time.\n\nIn some cases, especially with strong expertise in specific technologies or frameworks and proven success in previous roles, salaries can exceed this range. It\u2019s also worth noting that benefits and bonuses can significantly impact total compensation.\n\nFor the most accurate and current salary information, I recommend checking job boards, salary surveys specific to the tech industry, or consulting platforms such as Glassdoor or Payscale.",
